      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle stands as a definitive example of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched cabin appointments, reflects a history of uncompromising care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen that remains indistinguishable from new, offering an unparalleled driving experience for the sophisticated enthusiast.",
